lead_paragraph: Alex Galchenyuk got his second goal of the game 1:59 into overtime and the Montreal Canadiens beat the Dallas Stars 4-3 on Tuesday night to end a four-game skid.

headline.print_headline: Galchenyuk Gets Second Goal in OT, Canadiens Beat Stars 4-3
